# token-x-ray.tape — vhs script for the token-x-ray demo GIF.

Output "demos/token-x-ray.gif"

Set Theme "GitHub Dark"
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1180
Set Height 900
Set Padding 24
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set Framerate 24

Hide
Type "clear && bash demos/scenario-token-x-ray.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 18s
